What you need to know:

From Kwa Rhonda slums in Nakuru, Mwale wants to cut a niche for himself on the local scene before turning professional like his mentor, David Alaba, who plays for Bayern.Harambee Stars coach Mulee handed the Ulinzi Stars defender his first national team spot. The 25-year-old is adjusting to his new status and planning ahead to help Stars qualify for the 2022 World Cup in Qatar.On the local scene, he is making waves and his presence has been felt when Ulinzi needed him most.